snippet.title: Purps Plays: Func Xmas Jam 2017, part 2
snippet.description:
Three maps this time.
00:00 - Pale Signs of Doom by Breezeep
05:18 - Remains in a Manger by Dumptruck_ds
13:06 - The Drowning a City Fell Victim To by Mukor

Third part likely to contain the last 4 maps unless the last map is really, *really* long.
